{
  "id": "68aea1c67b107492fdd7af39",
  "title": "面積・体積・外積",
  "created": 1756275146,
  "updated": 1756284466,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "68aea1c67b107492fdd7af39",
      "text": "面積・体積・外積",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756275146,
      "updated": 1756275146
    },
    {
      "id": "68aea1c900000000001b17c5",
      "text": "ここでいう[外積]は[ウェッジ積]のこと",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756275146,
      "updated": 1756275162
    },
    {
      "id": "68aea1d900000000001b17c7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756275162,
      "updated": 1756275162
    },
    {
      "id": "68aea1d900000000001b17c8",
      "text": "面積や体積を高次元に一般化するにはどうすれば良いだろうか。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756275162,
      "updated": 1756275241
    },
    {
      "id": "68aea21900000000001b17c9",
      "text": "面積を考える際も、体積を考える際も、結局細かく分けた領域の面積や体積を測定して足し合わせる操作をする",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756275226,
      "updated": 1756275326
    },
    {
      "id": "68aea27d00000000001b17cb",
      "text": "\t→積分のこと",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756275326,
      "updated": 1756275336
    },
    {
      "id": "68aea28800000000001b17cc",
      "text": "よって、極めてシンプルな図形の面積や体積を考えておけば良いだろう。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756275336,
      "updated": 1756275373
    },
    {
      "id": "68aea2ac00000000001b17cd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756275373,
      "updated": 1756275373
    },
    {
      "id": "68aea2b200000000001b17ce",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756275378,
      "updated": 1756275378
    },
    {
      "id": "68aea32c00000000001b17cf",
      "text": "長方形と直方体の面積",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756275500,
      "updated": 1756275604
    },
    {
      "id": "68aea33d00000000001b17d0",
      "text": "\t2次元図形のうち、極めてシンプルなものといえば長方形である。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756275517,
      "updated": 1756275612
    },
    {
      "id": "68aea35600000000001b17d1",
      "text": "\t縦横の長さを[$ x,y]で表せば面積は[$ xy]となる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756275542,
      "updated": 1756275582
    },
    {
      "id": "68aea37f00000000001b17d2",
      "text": "\t3次元図形のうち、極めてシンプルなものといえば直方体である。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756275583,
      "updated": 1756275627
    },
    {
      "id": "68aea3ab00000000001b17d3",
      "text": "\t縦横奥行きの長さを[$ x,y,z]で表せば、面積は[$ xyz]となる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756275627,
      "updated": 1756275657
    },
    {
      "id": "68aea21a00000000001b17ca",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756275226,
      "updated": 1756275226
    },
    {
      "id": "68aea3ca00000000001b17d4",
      "text": "平行四辺形と平行六面体の面積",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756275659,
      "updated": 1756275676
    },
    {
      "id": "68aea3de00000000001b17d5",
      "text": "\tこれらの図形は長方形や直方体を歪ませたものである。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756275678,
      "updated": 1756275702
    },
    {
      "id": "68aea3f700000000001b17d6",
      "text": "\tその面積を求めるのは容易ではないが、図形が平行な線分で囲まれているという利点は残されている。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756275703,
      "updated": 1756275749
    },
    {
      "id": "68aea42500000000001b17d7",
      "text": "\t平行な線分を扱うためにベクトルを導入する。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756275750,
      "updated": 1756275772
    },
    {
      "id": "68aea46500000000001b17d8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756275813,
      "updated": 1756279237
    },
    {
      "id": "68aea51d00000000001b17d9",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/d7e03ae662b15d3cc117f95842978813]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756275997,
      "updated": 1756277674
    },
    {
      "id": "68aeabac00000000001b17de",
      "text": " \t[$ S(\\bm x,\\bm y+a\\bm x)=S(\\bm x,\\bm y)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756277676,
      "updated": 1756277719
    },
    {
      "id": "68aeab5000000000001b17dc",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/0f38656f2dbfeb5e9dc05f8999ea7da5]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756277585,
      "updated": 1756277675
    },
    {
      "id": "68aeabde00000000001b17df",
      "text": " \t[$ S(\\bm x,\\bm y+b\\bm y)=S(\\bm x,\\bm y)+S(\\bm x,b\\bm y)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756277727,
      "updated": 1756278374
    },
    {
      "id": "68aeac4300000000001b17e0",
      "text": " \t[$ S(\\bm x,k\\bm y)=kS(\\bm x,\\bm y)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756277828,
      "updated": 1756277858
    },
    {
      "id": "68aeaba300000000001b17dd",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/ba60ae8e835cbe81a3776ac27a8d532e]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756277668,
      "updated": 1756278013
    },
    {
      "id": "68aead0100000000001b17e2",
      "text": " \t[$ S(\\bm x,\\bm y+(a\\bm x+b\\bm y))=S(\\bm x,a\\bm x+(1+b)\\bm y)=S(\\bm x,(1+b)\\bm y)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756278018,
      "updated": 1756281085
    },
    {
      "id": "68aeb8fd00000000001b17f6",
      "text": " \t\t[$ =S(\\bm x,\\bm y)+S(\\bm x,b\\bm y)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756281085,
      "updated": 1756281087
    },
    {
      "id": "68aeacfd00000000001b17e1",
      "text": "\t[$ \\bm x]が潰れる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756278013,
      "updated": 1756280620
    },
    {
      "id": "68aeb04800000000001b17e3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756278856,
      "updated": 1756280616
    },
    {
      "id": "68aeb2b100000000001b17eb",
      "text": "平行六面体でも同様に、他の固定した成分と平行な成分が潰れる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756279474,
      "updated": 1756280684
    },
    {
      "id": "68aeb7c700000000001b17f1",
      "text": "\t[$ V(\\bm x,\\bm y,\\bm z+a\\bm x)=V(\\bm x,\\bm y,\\bm z)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756280775,
      "updated": 1756281169
    },
    {
      "id": "68aeb7e800000000001b17f2",
      "text": "\t[$ V(\\bm x,\\bm y,\\bm z+b\\bm y)=V(\\bm x,\\bm y,\\bm z)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756280808,
      "updated": 1756281173
    },
    {
      "id": "68aeb7f200000000001b17f3",
      "text": "\t[$ V(\\bm x,\\bm y,\\bm z+c\\bm z)=V(\\bm x,\\bm y,\\bm z)+V(\\bm x,\\bm y,c\\bm z)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756280819,
      "updated": 1756281182
    },
    {
      "id": "68aeb81400000000001b17f4",
      "text": "\t[$ V(\\bm x,\\bm y,k\\bm z)=kV(\\bm x,\\bm y,\\bm z)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756280852,
      "updated": 1756281186
    },
    {
      "id": "68aeb81900000000001b17f5",
      "text": "\t[$ V(\\bm x,\\bm y,\\bm z+(a\\bm x+b\\bm y+c\\bm z))=V(\\bm x,\\bm y,a\\bm x+b\\bm y+(1+c)\\bm z)=V(\\bm x,\\bm y,(1+c)\\bm z)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756280858,
      "updated": 1756281194
    },
    {
      "id": "68aeb91b00000000001b17f8",
      "text": "\t\t[$ =V(\\bm x,\\bm y,\\bm z)+V(\\bm x,\\bm y,c\\bm z)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756281115,
      "updated": 1756281202
    },
    {
      "id": "68aeab4c00000000001b17db",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756277581,
      "updated": 1756277581
    },
    {
      "id": "68aea51d00000000001b17da",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756275997,
      "updated": 1756281270
    },
    {
      "id": "68aeb9b700000000001b17fa",
      "text": "ここで、面積や体積について、1本のベクトルを動かす場合、それ以外のベクトルの成分は潰れてしまうため、線形性が成立する。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756281272,
      "updated": 1756281670
    },
    {
      "id": "68aeba0500000000001b17fb",
      "text": "\t[$ S(\\bm e_1,a\\bm x+b\\bm y)=S(\\bm e_1,a(x_1\\bm e_1+x_2\\bm e_2)+b(y_1\\bm e_1+y_2\\bm e_2))]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756281350,
      "updated": 1756281450
    },
    {
      "id": "68aeba7000000000001b17fc",
      "text": "\t\t[$ =S(\\bm e_1,(ax_1+by_1)\\bm e_1+(ax_2+by_2)\\bm e_2)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756281456,
      "updated": 1756281524
    },
    {
      "id": "68aebab600000000001b17fd",
      "text": "\t\t[$ =S(\\bm e_1,(ax_2+by_2)\\bm e_2)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756281527,
      "updated": 1756281551
    },
    {
      "id": "68aebada00000000001b17fe",
      "text": "\t\t[$ =(ax_2+by_2)S(\\bm e_1,\\bm e_2)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756281563,
      "updated": 1756281604
    },
    {
      "id": "68aebaf000000000001b17ff",
      "text": "\t\t[$ =ax_2S(\\bm e_1,\\bm e_2)+by_2S(\\bm e_1,\\bm e_2)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756281584,
      "updated": 1756281614
    },
    {
      "id": "68aebb2e00000000001b1800",
      "text": "\t\t[$ =aS(\\bm e_1,x_2\\bm e_2)+bS(\\bm e_1,y_2\\bm e_2)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756281647,
      "updated": 1756281692
    },
    {
      "id": "68aeb91f00000000001b17f9",
      "text": "\t[$ S(\\bm e_1,\\bm x)=S(\\bm e_1,x_1\\bm e_1+x_2\\bm e_2)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756281119,
      "updated": 1756282128
    },
    {
      "id": "68aebc1c00000000001b1804",
      "text": "\t\t[$ =S(\\bm e_1,x_2\\bm e_2)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756281885,
      "updated": 1756282516
    },
    {
      "id": "68aebc8a00000000001b1807",
      "text": "\t\t同様に、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756281994,
      "updated": 1756281998
    },
    {
      "id": "68aebc8d00000000001b1808",
      "text": "\t\t[$ S(\\bm e_1,\\bm y)=S(\\bm e_1,y_2\\bm e_2)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756281998,
      "updated": 1756282150
    },
    {
      "id": "68aebcc400000000001b1809",
      "text": "\t故に[$ S(\\bm e_1,a\\bm x+b\\bm y)=aS(\\bm e_1,\\bm x)+bS(\\bm e_1,\\bm y)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756282053,
      "updated": 1756282168
    },
    {
      "id": "68aebbcd00000000001b1803",
      "text": "\t[$ V(\\bm e_1,\\bm e_2,a\\bm x+b\\bm y)=V(\\bm e_1,\\bm e_2,ax_3\\bm e_3+by_3\\bm e_3)][$ \\because]これ以外の成分は潰れる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756281805,
      "updated": 1756282690
    },
    {
      "id": "68aebdcb00000000001b180b",
      "text": "\t\t[$ =V(\\bm e_1,\\bm e_2,(ax_3+by_3)\\bm e_3)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756282316,
      "updated": 1756282699
    },
    {
      "id": "68aebdf600000000001b180c",
      "text": "\t\t[$ =(ax_3+by_3)V(\\bm e_1,\\bm e_2,\\bm e_3)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756282359,
      "updated": 1756282704
    },
    {
      "id": "68aebe1800000000001b180d",
      "text": "\t\t[$ =ax_3V(\\bm e_1,\\bm e_2,\\bm e_3)+by_3V(\\bm e_1,\\bm e_2,\\bm e_3)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756282393,
      "updated": 1756282716
    },
    {
      "id": "68aebe2000000000001b180e",
      "text": "\t\t[$ =aV(\\bm e_1,\\bm e_2,x_3\\bm e_3)+bV(\\bm e_1,\\bm e_2,y_3\\bm e_3)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756282401,
      "updated": 1756282721
    },
    {
      "id": "68aebe4b00000000001b180f",
      "text": "\t[$ V(\\bm e_1,\\bm e_2,\\bm x)=V(\\bm e_1,\\bm e_2,x_1\\bm e_1+x_2\\bm e_2+x_3\\bm e_3)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756282443,
      "updated": 1756282492
    },
    {
      "id": "68aebe8400000000001b1810",
      "text": "  [$ =V(\\bm e_1,\\bm e_2,x_3\\bm e_3)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756282501,
      "updated": 1756282567
    },
    {
      "id": "68aebeaa00000000001b1811",
      "text": "  同様に、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756282539,
      "updated": 1756282583
    },
    {
      "id": "68aebed600000000001b1812",
      "text": "   [$ V(\\bm e_1,\\bm e_2,\\bm y)=V(\\bm e_1,\\bm e_2,y_3\\bm e_3)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756282583,
      "updated": 1756282583
    },
    {
      "id": "68aebd7400000000001b180a",
      "text": "\t故に[$ V(\\bm e_1,\\bm e_2,a\\bm x+b\\bm y)=aV(\\bm e_1,\\bm e_2,\\bm x)+bV(\\bm e_1,\\bm e_2,\\bm y)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756282229,
      "updated": 1756282740
    },
    {
      "id": "68aebee200000000001b1814",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756282595,
      "updated": 1756282595
    },
    {
      "id": "68aebf2500000000001b1815",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756282662,
      "updated": 1756282662
    },
    {
      "id": "68aebf7500000000001b1817",
      "text": "これらの考察から、超平行多面体の超体積(?)を求める計算について以下の公理を要請すると良さそうだ。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756282742,
      "updated": 1756284459
    },
    {
      "id": "68aebfbf00000000001b1818",
      "text": "\t[$ \\mu:\\R^n\\times\\cdots\\times \\R^n\\to\\R]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756282815,
      "updated": 1756282878
    },
    {
      "id": "68aec00500000000001b1819",
      "text": "\t多重線型性",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756282886,
      "updated": 1756282898
    },
    {
      "id": "68aec01200000000001b181a",
      "text": "\t\t[$ \\mu(a\\bm x+b\\bm y,\\bm c_2,\\cdots,\\bm c_n)=a\\mu(\\bm x,\\bm c_2,\\cdots,\\bm c_n)+b\\mu(\\bm y,\\bm c_2,\\cdots,\\bm c_3)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756282898,
      "updated": 1756282999
    },
    {
      "id": "68aec0fb00000000001b181b",
      "text": "\t\t他の引数についても同様に線形性が成立",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756283131,
      "updated": 1756283147
    },
    {
      "id": "68aec10d00000000001b181c",
      "text": "\t同じ元を引数に取ると0になる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756283150,
      "updated": 1756283199
    },
    {
      "id": "68aec14000000000001b181d",
      "text": "\t\t[$ \\mu(\\bm x,\\bm x,\\bm c_3,\\cdots,\\bm c_n)=0]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756283200,
      "updated": 1756283231
    },
    {
      "id": "68aebf2600000000001b1816",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756282663,
      "updated": 1756282663
    },
    {
      "id": "68aec17000000000001b181e",
      "text": "ここで、[ウェッジ積]は公理として多重線型性と交代性(同じ元を引数に取ると0になる)を持つ。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756283249,
      "updated": 1756283310
    },
    {
      "id": "68aec1ae00000000001b1821",
      "text": "\tよって、ウェッジ積は超体積を求める計算になる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756283310,
      "updated": 1756283341
    },
    {
      "id": "68aec1e100000000001b1822",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756283361,
      "updated": 1756283365
    },
    {
      "id": "68aec1e700000000001b1823",
      "text": "ウェッジ積は計算後の値に基底成分が残るが、その大きさが超体積(?)になると考えることができる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1756283367,
      "updated": 1756284466
    },
    {
      "id": "68aec22a00000000001b1824",
      "text": "\t[$ \\bm c_1\\wedge\\cdots\\wedge\\bm c_n=\\mu(\\bm c_1,\\cdots,\\bm c_n)(\\bm e_1\\wedge\\cdots\\wedge\\bm e_n)]",
